CINI -- C Project Initialization
================================

1. Install:

    $ git clone https://github.com/petervaro/cini.git
    $ cd cini
    $ sudo cp cini.sh /usr/local/bin/cini

2. Usage:

    # Create new project folder and initialize it
    $ cd path/to/parent/folder/of/project
    $ cini my-project
    $ cd my-project

    # Initialize an existing project folder
    $ cd path/to/the/project
    $ cini .
